Two of the rescuers jumped into the water with the dolphin and, seconds later, after the dolphin had stabilised himself, he “shot off” in the direction of his pod.
“It was a complete team effort and everybody was so ecstatic and so relieved. Definitely one of the highlights of my 20-year career,” said De Klerk.

The Mercury